ZH: 这只螃蟹的壳子很大。
EN: The shell of this crab is very big.

ZH: 小鸟在树枝上搭了一个小壳子。
EN: The little bird built a small nest on the tree branch.

ZH: 壳子里的蛋都破了。
EN: All the eggs inside the shell have cracked.

ZH: 他小心翼翼地捧着一个螺壳。
EN: He carefully held a seashell in his hands.

ZH: 这个贝壳是在海滩上捡到的。
EN: This seashell was found on the beach.

ZH: 她给我讲了一个关于她捡到的贝壳的故事。
EN: She told me a story about the seashell she found.

ZH: 这个蚌壳很坚固。
EN: This clamshell is very sturdy.

ZH: 她把壳子放在一个小盒子里保存着。
EN: She keeps the shells in a small box.

ZH: 这只龟的壳子很硬。
EN: The tortoise shell is very hard.

ZH: 墙上挂着一幅用贝壳制作的艺术品。
EN: There is a piece of artwork made from shells hanging on the wall.

ZH: 她把壳子串成了一条项链。
EN: She strung the shells together to make a necklace.

ZH: 我在沙滩上捡到了一个海螺壳。
EN: I found a conch shell on the beach.

ZH: 这些壳子的颜色非常鲜艳。
EN: The shells have very vibrant colors.

ZH: 她把沙滩上的贝壳都装进一个篮子里。
EN: She put all the seashells from the beach into a basket.

ZH: 海洋深处有很多奇怪形状的壳子。
EN: There are many strange-shaped shells in the depths of the ocean.

ZH: 小朋友们在沙地上堆了一个巨大的蚌壳。
EN: The children built a huge sandcastle in the shape of a clamshell.

ZH: 我们在海边拾了很多美丽的贝壳。
EN: We collected many beautiful shells at the seaside.

ZH: 这个壳子的质地很脆。
EN: The shell has a fragile texture.

ZH: 壳子里的珍珠闪闪发光。
EN: The pearls inside the shell are sparkling.

ZH: 她把壳子摆放在书架上，用来装饰。
EN: She put the shells on the bookshelf as decorations.
